queries.sql: SELECT `lrfoims_products`.*, `pc`.`product_description`, `ps`.`name`, `pd`.`name` as `description` FROM `lrfoims_products` JOIN `lrfoims_product_categories` as `pc` ON `pc`.`id` = `lrfoims_products`.`product_category_id` JOIN `lrfoims_product_measures` as `pd` ON `pd`.`id` = `lrfoims_products`.`product_description_id` JOIN `lrfoims_product_status` as `ps` ON `ps`.`id` = `lrfoims_products`.`product_status_id` WHERE `lrfoims_products`.`status` = 'a' AND `lrfoims_products`.`deleted_at` IS NULL ORDER BY `lrfoims_products`.`id` ASC

SELECT `lrfoims_ingredient_out`.*, SUM(lrfoims_ingredient_out.total_unit_price) as total, COUNT(lrfoims_ingredient_out.ingredient_id) as countIngredientReport, `p`.`product_name`, `p`.`id` as `product_id` FROM `lrfoims_ingredient_out` JOIN `lrfoims_products` as `p` ON `lrfoims_ingredient_out`.`ingredient_id` = `p`.`id` WHERE `lrfoims_ingredient_out`.`status` = 'a' AND `lrfoims_ingredient_out`.`deleted_at` IS NULL GROUP BY `lrfoims_ingredient_out`.`ingredient_id`

SELECT SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 1) AS Jan, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 2) AS Feb, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 3) AS Mar, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 4) AS Apr, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 5) AS May, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 6) AS Jun, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 7) AS Jul, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 8) AS Aug, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 9) AS Sept, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 10) AS Oct, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 11) AS Nov, SUM(MONTH(stock_out_date) = 12) AS December FROM `lrfoims_products` WHERE `status` = 'a' AND `lrfoims_products`.`deleted_at` IS NULL
